    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p> </p>\n<h2>Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Create read-only role or limit specific Cloud Console account permissions</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Scale Events Schedule is causing CPU and RAM spikes</span></li>\n<li>API is not terminating running processes when accessed by shell via CLI or UI</li>\n<li>Wait for startup to be completely finished before exposing port 3000</li>\n<li>Fixed Liferay-service fails to process license</li>\n<li>Fixed Liferay post start script hides error messages, but retains a non-zero exit code<span></span>\n</li>\n</ul>"
      },
